# Version Bumping

When bumping the NewsMinus version number, use the repo tool so all locations stay in sync:

```bash
python3 scripts/bump-version.py
```

This updates:

1. **`manifest.json`** — `"version"`
2. **`safari/NYTimesCleanerSafari.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj`** — `MARKETING_VERSION` and `CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION`
3. **`safari/scripts/gen_pbxproj.py`** — same version constants, then regenerates `project.pbxproj`

## Release levels

- **patch** (default) — bug fixes
- **minor** (`--minor`) — user-facing improvements
- **major** (`--major`) — breaking changes or newly supported sites in `manifest.json`

Do not hand-edit version strings in only one file.
